@item --with driver-echo
@itemx --without driver-echo
@opindex driver-echo

Enable building @file{echo} driver linked into @file{streams} object instead
built as a separate loadable kernel module.  The default is to create the driver
as a separate loadable kernel module.

@item --with driver-nuls
@itemx --without driver-nuls
@opindex driver-nuls

Enable building @file{nuls} driver linked into @file{streams} object instead
