@item --with driver-pipe
@itemx --without driver-pipe
@opindex driver-pipe

Enable building @file{pipe} driver linked into @file{streams} object instead
built as a separate loadable kernel module.  The default is to create the driver
as a separate loadable kernel module.

@item --with driver-log
@itemx --without driver-log
@opindex driver-log

Enable building @file{log} driver linked into @file{streams} object instead
built as a separate loadable kernel module.  The default is to create the driver
as a separate loadable kernel module.

@item --with streams-fifos
@itemx --without streams-fifos
@opindex streams-fifos

Enable override of system fifos with STREAMS-based fifos.
The default for this feature is disabled.

@end table

